{"tid":1558233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"本人發誓911沒有任何反送中示威活動，任何事發生必為中，港共陷阱","createTime":"2019-09-10T11:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T00:03:04.000Z","uid":136992,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"225077dceefa5d17029e118f6dfaf10ee60060f3","tid":1558233,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"911美國國殤日，<br />\n本人發誓911沒有任何反送中示威活動，<br />\n示威者會為美國人默哀祈禱<br />\n明天9月11所有示威活動或襲擊，並非反送中示威者行動，<br />\n任何事發生必為中，港共陷阱<br />\n<br />\nI swear that there are no anti-extradition bill protests on 11/9.<br />\nWe,protestors, will pray for all American.<br />\nAny protests or attacks happen on tomorrow 11/9, are not related to our protestors. It is the trap organized by China and Hong Kong gov to defame protestors.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyx317A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpyx317A.jpg&h=39282d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事源<br />\n突發！發現9月11日港共既劇本<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahbGxAU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahbGxAU</a>"},{"pid":"b0e7dcd2b12f974350fb763509ffc9f118d60ef0","tid":1558233,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:35:30.000Z","msg":"911"},{"pid":"110d8497ad63b5683e680767c7fe47610e618afc","tid":1558233,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:36:05.000Z","msg":"911"},{"pid":"373c1b338b88666df816f1bb326477de2ab93bf7","tid":1558233,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"911"},{"pid":"3f267b04ad5eb4cb1fd4699d3073d3fd848a5089","tid":1558233,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"Reddit有冇"},{"pid":"d20f487f304e2370f203c40421f6020bee3d9b66","tid":1558233,"uid":160075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:36:39.000Z","msg":"911"},{"